                <lb n="b1x" commRef="n2"/> ṣek somotkäñe yamaṣäṃ <lb n="b2x" commRef="n3 n4"/> pa p <lb n="b3x"/> ·e <lac aks="1"/> mp· <lb n="b3y" commRef="n5"/> kakraupau <lb n="b3z" commRef="n6"/> tu (ai)śamo <lb n="b5x"/>
